            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "亞洲股市追隨華爾街漲勢攀升;日經指數創歷史新高,中國GDP超預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zjSDEtzkeZRfvN.lcao2Lw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB310J3_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週四亞洲股市延續強勁漲勢,日本日經指數創下歷史新高,投資者受華爾街創紀錄收盤提振,同時評估中國超出預期的經濟增長數據。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隔夜華爾街收於歷史高位,標普500指數和納斯達克指數均刷新高峰。此輪漲勢由強勁的企業財報和美國與伊朗緊張局勢可能通過重啟外交努力而緩和的樂觀情緒推動。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>日本日經指數創歷史新高;南韓KOSPI指數大漲</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本日經225指數攀升2.6%至歷史新高59,624.0點,而更廣泛的東證指數上漲1.3%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-00be55d6-297e-3b9a-b5a0-87e10b17a736-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">科技股和晶片相關股領漲,人工智能需求持續樂觀情緒提振市場信心。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">南韓KOSPI指數也上漲超過2%,接近今年稍早創下的歷史高點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國與伊朗和平談判取得進展的希望近日幫助穩定全球風險情緒,緩解了對能源供應中斷和通脹壓力的擔憂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,華盛頓已對伊朗港口實施全面海上封鎖,美國軍隊對進出伊朗的船隻實施限制,並在霍爾木茲海峽附近部署大量海軍資產。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新加坡海峽時報指數下跌0.2%,而與印度Nifty 50指數掛鉤的期貨持平。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>中國第一季GDP超預期;澳洲就業增長放緩</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國樂觀的經濟數據進一步支撐亞洲投資者信心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全球第二大經濟體第一季同比增長5.0%,超出4.8%的預期,較上一季的4.5%有所改善。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四公布的其他活動數據描繪出喜憂參半但仍具韌性的圖景。中國3月工業生產較去年同期增長5.7%,超過5.4%的預期增幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">衡量消費的關鍵指標零售銷售3月增長1.7%,低於1.9%的預期增幅,凸顯國內需求持續疲軟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國上證綜合指數上漲0.4%,而藍籌股滬深300指數上漲0.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">香港恒生指數攀升超過1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時,澳洲勞動力市場數據顯示,3月失業率維持在4.3%,就業溫和增長,全職職位增幅保持強勁,顯示儘管招聘有所放緩,但基本面仍具韌性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四澳洲標普/ASX 200指數下跌0.2%,與更廣泛的區域趨勢背道而馳。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E8%BF%BD%E9%9A%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%BC%B2%E5%8B%A2%E6%94%80%E5%8D%87-%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%93%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E5%89%B5%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8Bgdp%E8%B6%85%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-041105218.html",
