        {
            "title": "中方施壓｜傳中國發改委曾召見 要求馬士基及MSC退出巴拿馬港口營運",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"560\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fz1DANNj0qQoXt8UbnvUtw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/95f7e3565e80862ce934b69ce311b255\" width=\"840\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"英國《金融時報》\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:英國《金融時報》;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/英國《金融時報》\">英國《金融時報》</a>引述消息報道，就<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"巴拿馬\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:巴拿馬;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/巴拿馬\">巴拿馬</a>早前政府撤銷長和（001）旗下巴拿馬港口公司（PPC）在當地兩個港口的經營權，並交由兩大歐洲航運企業<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"馬士基\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:馬士基;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/馬士基\">馬士基</a>（Maersk）及地中海航運公司（MSC）接手後，中國發改委上月曾召見兩間公司代表，要求其立即退出巴拿馬運河兩側港口的營運。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報道指，發改委向馬士基及MSC代表表明，要求他們立即撤出巴拿馬運河沿線的巴爾博亞（Balboa）及克里斯托瓦爾（Cristobal）港口營運，並要求兩間航運公司「不要從事損害中國公司利益的非法活動」，遵守商業道德及國際規則；而馬士基與MSC強調，獲臨時經營權是為維持巴拿馬運河的貿易暢通。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-aba275ca-a4e7-3f36-a694-86b100c494c5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，交通部警告，在美伊戰事對供應鏈造成干擾下，兩間公司須保持供應鏈暢通。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">巴拿馬法院早前裁定，長和旗下的巴拿馬港口公司（Panama Ports Company，PPC）在當地的兩港口合約違憲，強制接管港口設施及沒收其財產，並交由馬士基及MSC各自臨時經營一個港口。長和強調，相關行動不合法，將採取法律應對措施，並已分別向巴拿馬政府、馬士基啟動國際介裁程序。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93-%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E6%94%B9%E5%A7%94%E6%9B%BE%E5%8F%AC%E8%A6%8B-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%A6%AC%E5%A3%AB%E5%9F%BA%E5%8F%8Amsc%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E5%B7%B4%E6%8B%BF%E9%A6%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B-033231419.html",
